---
/**
 * /alder/kairos — Alder · Kairos flagship product page.
 *
 * Kairos = protocols, labs, cadence — one household, one plan.
 * For wellness-forward founders · Helios crossover line item.
 *
 * Voice: calm · evidence-first · patient. Accent: #a7f3d0 (mint) on deep navy.
 */
import AtlasLayout from "../../layouts/AtlasLayout.astro";
import AgentTile from "../../components/atlas/AgentTile.astro";
import { getHolding } from "../../data/atlas";

const alder = getHolding("alder")!;
---

<AtlasLayout
  title="Kairos — Alder · LYRA"
  description="Protocols, labs, cadence — one household, one plan. Alder's longevity terminal."
  active="alder"
>
  <!-- ────────────── HERO — calm register ────────────── -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden border-b border-white/5">
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
      style="background: radial-gradient(1100px 600px at 22% 20%, rgba(167, 243, 208, 0.11), transparent 60%), radial-gradient(760px 480px at 82% 72%, rgba(74, 110, 184, 0.07), transparent 62%);"
    ></div>

    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-[84rem] px-6 py-24 sm:py-32">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.22em] uppercase text-ink-500">
        <a href="/atlas" class="hover:text-white transition">Atlas</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <a href="/alder" class="hover:text-white transition">Alder</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <span class="text-ink-300">Kairos</span>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="kicker">Flagship · 05.00</span>
        <span class="tag tag-accent">● live</span>
        <span class="label-xs">PAGE · CHAPTER · VOLUME</span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="mt-8 font-display text-[clamp(3rem,10vw,8rem)] font-light leading-[0.9] tracking-tight text-white">
        Kairos
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl font-display text-2xl italic font-light text-ink-200/90">
        Protocols, labs, cadence — one household, one plan.
      </p>

      <div class="hairline mt-8 max-w-md"></div>

      <p class="mt-8 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-ink-200 lede">
        Your body is a portfolio. Most founders run it by feel. Kairos runs
        it by lab work — biomarkers every quarter, protocols adjusted weekly,
        a cadence you actually keep. Not another tracker. The agent your
        physician would build if they had the time.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
        <a href="/join" class="btn-primary">Request access →</a>
        <a href="#how" class="btn-ghost">How it works</a>
        <a href="#pricing" class="btn-link">Pricing ↓</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Stat strip -->
      <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 border-t border-white/5 pt-8 sm:grid-cols-4">
        <div>
          <div class="label-xs">Biomarker cadence</div>
          <div class="mt-1 data-num text-3xl font-light text-white">quarterly</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="label-xs">Protocol review</div>
          <div class="mt-1 data-num text-3xl font-light text-white">weekly</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="label-xs">Household scope</div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-200">adults + minors · shared protocols</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="label-xs">Target operator</div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-200">P5 · Helios crossover</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ────────────── BEFORE / AFTER ────────────── -->
  <section class="border-b border-white/5">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[84rem] px-6 py-20">
      <div class="kicker mb-3">What Kairos replaces</div>
      <h2 class="page-title">One plan, not five apps.</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-sm text-ink-400">
        Longevity is a full-time job you don't want to have. Kairos is the
        plan that survives a travel week, a sick kid, a board meeting, and
        the 2 AM supplement question.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        <!-- BEFORE -->
        <div class="surface-warm p-8">
          <div class="label-xs text-ink-500">Before · the longevity stack</div>
          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-300">
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="font-mono text-ink-500">—</span>Function Health · Levels · MyFitnessPal · Whoop · Oura</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="font-mono text-ink-500">—</span>$25k/yr concierge MD you see three times a year</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="font-mono text-ink-500">—</span>A supplement spreadsheet that's six months out of date</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="font-mono text-ink-500">—</span>Lab results in five PDFs you can't compare</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="font-mono text-ink-500">—</span>A spouse running the same stack, separately</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <!-- AFTER -->
        <div class="surface p-8" style="border-color: color-mix(in oklab, #a7f3d0 28%, rgba(255,255,255,0.06));">
          <div class="label-xs" style="color: #a7f3d0;">After · Kairos</div>
          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-200">
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="font-mono" style="color:#a7f3d0;">●</span>Intake: biomarkers, history, goals · baseline in one pass</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="font-mono" style="color:#a7f3d0;">●</span>Protocol: the plan · adjusted weekly · plain language</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="font-mono" style="color:#a7f3d0;">●</span>Labs: order, read, remember · trends not one-offs</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="font-mono" style="color:#a7f3d0;">●</span>Cadence: the streaks that actually matter · not every streak</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="font-mono" style="color:#a7f3d0;">●</span>Concierge-M: book the doctor, the flight, the meal</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ────────────── SUB-AGENTS ────────────── -->
  <section class="border-b border-white/5">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[84rem] px-6 py-20">
      <div class="kicker mb-3">Inside Kairos</div>
      <h2 class="page-title">Nine agents. One household.</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-xl text-sm text-ink-400">
        Shared biomarkers, shared protocols, shared cadence — with the
        privacy boundaries a family needs.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        {alder.agents.map((a) => (
          <AgentTile agent={a} holdingSlug="alder" />
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ────────────── HOW IT WORKS ────────────── -->
  <section id="how" class="border-b border-white/5">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[84rem] px-6 py-20">
      <div class="kicker mb-3">How it works</div>
      <h2 class="page-title">Intake · Protocol · Labs · Cadence.</h2>

      <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
        <div class="surface p-6">
          <div class="label-xs" style="color:#a7f3d0;">01 · Intake</div>
          <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-ink-200">
            Biomarkers, history, goals. Baseline blood panel plus optional
            ApoB, LP(a), hsCRP, HOMA-IR. Family history surfaced; wearable
            data optional.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="surface p-6">
          <div class="label-xs" style="color:#a7f3d0;">02 · Protocol</div>
          <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-ink-200">
            The plan: sleep window, training split, nutrition targets, the
            three supplements that have evidence, the two that don't.
            Reviewed weekly, not quarterly.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="surface p-6">
          <div class="label-xs" style="color:#a7f3d0;">03 · Labs</div>
          <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-ink-200">
            Order on cadence. Read in trends, not absolutes. Flag what's
            moving wrong before it becomes a number your MD worries about.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="surface p-6">
          <div class="label-xs" style="color:#a7f3d0;">04 · Cadence</div>
          <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-ink-200">
            The streaks that matter: sleep window kept, training sessions
            loaded, ApoB trending down. The rest we ignore. The point is
            to keep the plan, not to have the most metrics.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ────────────── TERMINAL PREVIEW ────────────── -->
  <section class="border-b border-white/5" data-page="app">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[84rem] px-6 py-20">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 lg:grid-cols-5 lg:items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-2">
          <div class="kicker mb-3">Terminal</div>
          <h2 class="section-title">Monday morning, household K-0007.</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-ink-400">
            One screen. Two adults, two minors. What moved, what's off, what
            needs a decision this week.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-3">
          <div class="surface corner-ticks p-8"
               style="border-color: color-mix(in oklab, #a7f3d0 26%, rgba(255,255,255,0.06));">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="label-xs" style="color:#a7f3d0;">KAIROS · HOUSEHOLD K-0007 · MON 06:40</span>
              <span class="tag tag-accent">● live</span>
            </div>
            <pre class="mt-6 whitespace-pre-wrap font-mono text-[12.5px] leading-relaxed text-ink-200">
$ lyra kairos brief

┌─ Household ──────────────────────────────────
│ Adults .... 2   ·   Minors .... 2
│ Protocols . active  ·  reviewed Sat
│ Next labs . 14 days (ApoB + hsCRP panel)
└──────────────────────────────────────────────

$ lyra kairos trends --quarter

  Principal
  <span style="color:#a7f3d0;">●</span> VO2max ........ +3 / qtr  ·  on track
  <span style="color:#a7f3d0;">▲</span> ApoB .......... 92   ·  target 80  ·  <span style="color:#a7f3d0;">flagged</span>
  <span style="color:#a7f3d0;">●</span> HRV ........... 58   ·  stable band

$ lyra kairos flags

  Needs you
  <span style="color:#a7f3d0;">▲</span> Sleep debt: 4.2 hr last 7d  ·  window missed x3
  <span style="color:#a7f3d0;">▲</span> Spouse travel Thu–Sun  ·  protocol handoff ready
  ·  Minor-A annual well-visit overdue 8 days

$ lyra kairos next

  Tue 06:30 ... Zone-2 loaded  ·  45 min
  Wed 17:00 ... Lab draw booked  ·  Quest, Berkeley
  Sat 09:00 ... Weekly review with Dr. N

  <span class="text-ink-500">// static preview. live terminal lands with the first household.</span>
</pre>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ────────────── USE CASE ────────────── -->
  <section class="border-b border-white/5">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[84rem] px-6 py-20">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 md:grid-cols-5 md:items-start">
        <div class="md:col-span-2">
          <div class="kicker mb-3">Flagship use case</div>
          <h2 class="section-title">A founder household, nine months in.</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-ink-400">Anonymized. Real labs. Kairos's canonical pilot.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-3 space-y-6">
          <div class="surface p-6">
            <div class="label-xs">00 · The setup</div>
            <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-ink-200">
              Two adults, 38 & 41. Two minors. Previously on Function Health
              + Levels + a concierge MD at $28k/yr. Wearables: Oura, Whoop.
              Goal: the plan that survives a travel-heavy quarter.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="surface p-6">
            <div class="label-xs">01 · Month one</div>
            <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-ink-200">
              Intake done in a single evening. Baseline panel ordered to
              Quest. Protocol loaded. Wearable feeds unified. First weekly
              review on a Saturday morning — 18 minutes, not an hour.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="surface p-6">
            <div class="label-xs">02 · Month six</div>
            <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-ink-200">
              ApoB down 14 points (both adults). Sleep window kept 5/7
              average · up from 2/7. Minors on family-wide sleep window.
              MD visit cadence cut from 4× to 2×/yr — MD has the trend
              read they used to pay for.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="surface p-6" style="border-color: color-mix(in oklab, #a7f3d0 26%, rgba(255,255,255,0.06));">
            <div class="label-xs" style="color:#a7f3d0;">03 · Month twelve</div>
            <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-ink-200">
              Total wellness-line cost: $8.8k/yr vs. $36k legacy stack.
              Kairos is the household's plan of record. Shows up on Crest
              as a line item; protocols don't change when travel does.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ────────────── PRICING ────────────── -->
  <section id="pricing" class="border-b border-white/5">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[84rem] px-6 py-20">
      <div class="kicker mb-3">Pricing · Kairos</div>
      <h2 class="page-title">Three ways to begin.</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-xl text-sm text-ink-400">
        {alder.model}
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
        {alder.pricing.map((p, i) => (
          <div
            class={`surface p-8 ${i === 1 ? "md:-translate-y-2" : ""}`}
            style={i === 1 ? "border-color: color-mix(in oklab, #a7f3d0 34%, rgba(255,255,255,0.06));" : ""}
          >
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
              <div class="label-xs">{p.tier}</div>
              {i === 1 && <span class="tag tag-accent">Recommended</span>}
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6 font-display text-4xl font-light text-white data-num">{p.price}</div>
            <p class="mt-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-ink-300">{p.for}</p>
            <a href="/join" class={i === 1 ? "btn-primary mt-8 inline-block" : "btn-ghost mt-8 inline-block"}>
              Request access
            </a>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <p class="mt-8 max-w-2xl text-xs leading-relaxed text-ink-500">
        Lab costs pass through at provider rates. VOLUME adds Concierge-M
        — the booking layer that handles doctors, flights, and meals on
        the protocol.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ────────────── INTEGRATIONS ────────────── -->
  <section class="border-b border-white/5">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[84rem] px-6 py-16">
      <div class="kicker mb-3">Integrations</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Reads labs. Reads wearables. Reads you.</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 max-w-xl text-sm text-ink-400">
        The tools you already have. No new device to buy.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6">
        {[
          "Quest", "Labcorp", "Function Health (import)", "Whoop", "Oura",
          "Eight Sleep", "Apple Health", "Strava", "Levels",
          "Crest (household)", "Fidelis Receipt", "Concierge-M"
        ].map((n) => (
          <div class="surface px-4 py-3 text-center">
            <div class="font-mono text-[11px] tracking-wider text-ink-300">{n}</div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ────────────── CROSS-HOLDING CALLS ────────────── -->
  <section class="border-b border-white/5">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[84rem] px-6 py-16">
      <div class="kicker mb-3">Where Kairos listens</div>
      <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="surface p-5">
          <div class="label-xs" style="color:#a7f3d0;">↔ Helios · Crest</div>
          <p class="mt-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-ink-200">
            Household line item on the family portfolio. Succession
            reviews reference the protocol record.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="surface p-5">
          <div class="label-xs" style="color:#a7f3d0;">↔ Tide · Marea</div>
          <p class="mt-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-ink-200">
            Wellness-forward hotel brands cross-refer guests into Kairos
            as part of stay packages.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="surface p-5">
          <div class="label-xs" style="color:#a7f3d0;">↔ Fidelis · Receipt</div>
          <p class="mt-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-ink-200">
            Labs, MD visits, supplements route to HSA/FSA-eligible
            categorization in Ledger.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ────────────── CTA ────────────── -->
  <section>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[84rem] px-6 py-24">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between">
        <div>
          <div class="kicker mb-3">Design partner cohort</div>
          <h2 class="page-title">Kairos opens with twelve households.</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 max-w-xl text-sm text-ink-300">
            Wellness-forward founders. Crossover with Helios households
            welcomed. Minors supported from the first day.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <a href="/join" class="btn-primary">Apply as a household →</a>
          <a href="/alder" class="btn-ghost">Back to Alder</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</AtlasLayout>
